body:
1.The communication protocol between AndroidAPS and the Equil pump was updated to correctly handle insulin doses of 10 units or higher. Additionally, a validation check was implemented in AndroidAPS to ensure that doses are within the Equil pump's supported range before initiating the injection.
 2.Fixed When insulin reservoirs will become empty and piston is going back, AndroidAPS app still shows progress of injection of insulin

https://github.com/nightscout/AndroidAPS/issues/3467
